        {
          "component_id": "artifact_list",
          "data": {
            "circlet_of_logos": {
              "desc": "<p>草木的主神贈送的冠冕，曾在迷宮的王之間代代相傳，最終由王的侍者繼承。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/26/7998136/11abc6739dff1cf50b95b394a3462162_2011232243269201212.png",
              "id": "artifact26481",
              "key": "circlet_of_logos",
              "posKey": "circlet_of_logos",
              "posName": "理之冠",
              "position": "理之冠",
              "title": "月桂的寶冠"
            },
            "flower_of_life": {
              "desc": "<p>從森林王的寶冠上摘下的飾金之花。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/26/7998136/f526e111c9c7dcbaed0d7fd8c8d58ef2_5273255852889023739.png",
              "id": "artifact19805",
              "key": "flower_of_life",
              "posKey": "flower_of_life",
              "posName": "生之花",
              "position": "生之花",
              "title": "迷宮的遊人"
            },
            "goblet_of_eonothem": {
              "desc": "<p>本是沙漠形制的油燈，但其上生出了蒼翠螢光的綠葉。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/26/7998136/80ddb6398975e6b891e383a30079b873_5479561256410933034.png",
              "id": "artifact92944",
              "key": "goblet_of_eonothem",
              "posKey": "goblet_of_eonothem",
              "posName": "空之杯",
              "position": "空之杯",
              "title": "迷誤者之燈"
            },
            "plume_of_death": {
              "desc": "<p>飄逸如羽的翠色葉片，取自林中智者的衣衫。</p>",
              "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/08/26/7998136/9339ebbf175d61844f0b4fafddf7c601_3765592396517525580.png",
